item_category: The Galaxy S10 takes the classic S series a giant leap further. It features a large curved-edge screen and puts vault-like security at your fingertips with our new Ultrasonic Fingerprint Scanner. With a front camera and 3 rear cameras, including an ultra-wide and ultra-zoom lens, it's easy to capture every angle of a scene. It also comes with a battery with so much power you'll be able to share it with your friends.
